Package: datafaro
Title: Interact with the Datafaro API Seamlessly
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Daniel E.", "de la Rosa", , "me@dnldelarosa.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5965-5277")),
    person(given = "Datafaro",
           role = "cph"))
Description: DataFaro offers access to recurrent data from a variety of sources. 
    It abstracts concerns related to data frequency, format, and publication calendar. 
    This package provides a convenient wrapper for interacting with the Datafaro API, 
    making it easier for R users to harness the power of DataFaro.
